OL,7,FCCTV footage shows a serial Greggs
OL,8,Fthief nicknamed 'Hamster' by staff
OL,9,Fstealing drinks in plain sight.
OL,11,FAdam Gosling, 39, was spared jail
OL,12,Fafter admitting to stealing from a
OL,13,Fbranch of the bakery chain in
OL,14,FGreenford, west London, 38 times
OL,15,Fbetween December 30 2025 and February
OL,16,F10.
OL,18,FThe value of the thefts ranged from
OL,19,F#12.30 to #100 per visit and, on some
OL,20,Fdays, he targeted the shop multiple
OL,21,Ftimes, the charge sheet said.
