OL,7,FProsecutors told Uxbridge Magistrates'
OL,8,FCourt on Tuesday that Gosling's six-
OL,9,Fweek theft spree amounted to #1,817.50.
OL,11,FFootage released by the Metropolitan
OL,12,FPolice shows Gosling brazenly taking
OL,13,Fdrinks from a shop fridge.
OL,15,FIn one clip, wearing a hood over a
OL,16,Fcap, he fills a carrier bag with
OL,17,Fmultiple Lucozade bottles while a
OL,18,Fstaff member is at a nearby fridge.
OL,20,FThe staff member then enters a back
OL,21,Fdoor and Gosling walks out.
