OL,7,FIn another clip, Gosling, this time
OL,8,Fwith a face covering, is seen
OL,9,Fcontinuing to swipe drinks from the
OL,10,Ffridge as a staff member leans in,
OL,11,Fseemingly trying to check his face.The
OL,12,Fstaff member leaves through the same
OL,13,Fback door, and Gosling exits the shop.
OL,15,FA third clip shows him emptying the
OL,16,Ffridge of Lucozade bottles and taking
OL,17,Fother drinks.
