OL,7,FA staff member appears to notice him,
OL,8,Fenters the back door, and returns with
OL,9,Fa tablet ` but Gosling simply walks
OL,10,Fpast and exits the shop, leaving the
OL,11,Ffridge door open.
OL,13,FScotland Yard's Greenford Broadway
OL,14,Fsafer neighbourhood team said on its
OL,15,FMet Engage platform that staff saw a
OL,16,Fhigh number of thefts of food and
OL,17,Fdrink at the branch and began to log
OL,18,Feach one.
