OL,7,FPolice community support officer James
OL,8,FTupman said one man ` nicknamed
OL,9,F"Hamster" by staff ` became the "most
OL,10,Fprolific" thief.
OL,12,FOfficers identified him as Gosling
OL,13,Fthrough the CCTV footage and arrested
OL,14,Fhim on February 10.
OL,16,FThe defendant, who the court heard is
OL,17,Fcurrently homeless, had pleaded guilty
OL,18,Fto 38 counts of theft from a shop.
