OL,7,FChairwoman of the magistrates' bench
OL,8,FJudy Gregg sentenced him to four
OL,9,Fmonths, suspended for one year.
OL,11,FSuperintendent Sean Lynch, who leads
OL,12,Fneighbourhood policing in Ealing,
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are committed to tackling
OL,14,Fissues that have a real impact on
OL,15,Fbusinesses and communities ` including
OL,16,Fshoplifting.
OL,18,F"In the last year, theft offences have
OL,19,Ffallen by 8.3% in Ealing and 9.5%
OL,20,Facross the Met as a whole.
