OL,7,F"While we recognise there is more to
OL,8,Fdo to continue to drive down crime,
OL,9,Four officers will continue to work
OL,10,Fwith their communities and businesses
OL,11,Fto tackle repeat offenders and bring
OL,12,Fthem to justice."
OL,14,FMr Tupman wrote after he was charged:
OL,15,F"This result is the direct outcome of
OL,16,Fstrong partnership work with Greggs
OL,17,Fstaff, who have been exceptionally
OL,18,Fproactive in recording offences and
OL,19,Fsupporting our investigation.
